    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
先刻御見うけ申候通りニ、大兄の反したまふより<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">援</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ママ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>隊壮士三四等、ときの声を出し、ゑい／＼と押来り、くおふるに女軍吾本<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">陳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ママ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>お打破り其声百雷の（如）く、大兄此時ニもれたまふて、地下に吾に何の御<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">顔</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">カホ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を見セたまふや。御心根御為<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>聞<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>遣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（つかはさるべく）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>候。なぜに来りたまハぬや、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">御為<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>聞</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（おきかせ）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<lb />
<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">拝首。</span>
<span rend="superscript" rendition="sup">呈</span>佐々木将軍<lb />
<span rend="jisage_5" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 5em"><span type="ruby"><span type="rb">陳</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ママ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>下<span rend="chitsuki_1" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 1em">楳　拝首</span></span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
